lyrics:
Оооо, сердце тревогой окутал перестрой 2024 года
Оооо, зажгли в душе тоску и свет эксбоо
Оооо, сталкрафт горькой сладостью овеял

[verse]
Oh sweet Schanson, melodies divine
You fill my heart with love, like aged wine
Your stories woven through each note you sing
In your embrace, my soul takes flight, I'm free

[chorus]
Schanson, Schanson, let your voice ring true
Through ups and downs, I'll always turn to you
Schanson, Schanson, take me on a journey
In your timeless songs, my troubles find sanctuary
